                    <lb n="1"/>Λικίνις Ἰσαυ
                   <lb n="2" break="no"/>ρος ζῶν ὢν
                    <lb n="3"/>ἐποίει ἑαυτῷ
                    <lb n="4"/>καὶ τοῖς ἰδίοις
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp><app><note>Text after Zavettieri 2017</note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Likinis Isauros made this while still living for himself and his family</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="Zavettieri">
                <p>Licinio Isauro mentre era in vita faceva per se stesso e per i suoi familiari</p>
